<br>
There isn't any convention you have to stick to; just use whatever seems right for you.  A lot of us just don't like to use the word level - it sounds a little too mechanical, I guess.  The words you use to describe yourself are yours, use every little chance you have to paint a little more about you!<br>
<br>
That said, I also have used the term &quot;tier&quot; for clerics and warriors, and &quot;circle&quot; for rogues.  Doesn't really matter, we will figure out what you mean!<br>
<br>
Think away - then jump right in!  ^_^ <p>Titaisia<BR>
Circle of Sisters<BR>
Jharin apprentice of her 21st measure<BR>
